@startuml
title Viaverse AI Assistant Request — Activity Diagram
start
:User asks AI;
:Check session and capability;
:Classify intent\nsupport/search/safety/action;
:Build minimal context\nredacted + scoped;
:Privacy guard\nPII/secret redaction;
:Retrieve KB/domain docs\nif needed;
if (Risky action?) then (yes)
  :Escalate to human\ncreate ticket;
else (no)
  :Compose prompt\nwith policy boundaries;
  :Call LLM/model\nwith timeout/budget;
  :Output moderation\npolicy + hallucination checks;
  if (Safe/confident?) then (yes)
    :Return answer\nwith source hints;
  else (no)
    :Fallback answer\nor human handoff;
  endif
endif
:Log privacy-safe event\nfeedback hook;
stop

note bottom
Use minimal context and redaction before model call.
Do not put full private chat, payment data,
raw identity documents or secrets into prompts.
end note
@enduml
